item.description:
Join us for dinner and drinks at the newly opened Margaritas restaurant in Framingham (formerly Naked Fish location). Margaritas has great drinks and really good Mexican food. Have a fun and relaxing time and meet new and friendly people. We look forward to seeing you!

Everyone pays for their own food/drinks. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside entrance or at our table. Please call 774 232 0000 if you have trouble finding us.
item.name: Dinner and Drinks at new Margaritas Restaurant, Framingham
